name: Virgo
description:
Virgo is a constellation of the zodiac. Located between Leo to the west and Libra to the east, this constellation is one of the largest constellations in the sky. Virgo can be found easily through her star, Spica.

In the Zodiac, individuals who have the star Virgo, born on August 23 to September 22, when the sun is on the star Virgo.
